			<div class="kicker">Commentary</div>
	
	<h1 id="single-title" class="main-title">Molly Crabapple: How &#8216;broken windows&#8217; policing harms people of&nbsp;color</h1>

	
	<div>
		<span class="byline">by <a href="http://fusion.net/author/molly-crabapple/">Molly Crabapple</a></span> <span class="date">| February 3, 2015</span>
	</div>
</div>

</header>


<div id="single-content" class="row main-content">

	<div class="columns large-2 show-for-large-up article-meta">
	<div class="article-date">February 3, 2015</div>
	<div class="article-authors">
			<div class="article-author-card">
		<div class="article-author-pic">
			<div class="avatar-container"><a href="http://fusion.net/author/molly-crabapple/"><img width="90" height="90" src="http://i1.wp.com/fusiondotnet.files.wordpress.com/2014/11/sidebar_molly.jpg?resize=90%2C90&amp;quality=80&amp;strip=all" class="avatar photo avatar-90" alt="Molly Crabapple" width="90" height="90" /></a></div>
		</div>
		<div class="article-author-info">
			<h2 class="article-author-card-title"><a href="http://fusion.net/author/molly-crabapple/">Molly Crabapple</a></h2>

								<ul class="article-author-card-social inline-nav">
													<li><a target="_blank" class="icon-twitter-black" data-trigger="click" data-category="Button" data-action="Follow Twitter" data-label="author" href="https://twitter.com/intent/follow?screen_name=mollycrabapple&#038;original_referer=http://fusion.net"><span>twitter</span></a></li>
																							</ul>
			
							<div class="article-author-card-description"><p>Molly is a contributor to Fusion.</p>
</div>
					</div>
	</div>
	</div>
	<div class="article-share">
		
